				<p>We are THE go-to place for people to rent and lease-to-own items within the context of community around growing the Sharing Economy. To make a positive impact both in the lives of members and those served through partnerships and causes that make a difference that <a class="in-flink" href="{{ path('sylius_homepage') }}">kulashare&trade;</a> aligns itself with.
